701802f-a.title: Bronx: Soundview Avenue - White Plains Road
701802f-a.text:
Soundview Avenue, west side, at White Plains Road.
The Clason's Point bungalow colony and the Clason's Point
Amusement Park can be seen to the right and left of the
store, respectively.
July 29, 1928
Views 1, 2
P. L. Sperr
